Paid-up capital (baht)                   : 1,000,000,000.00
IPO shares (shares)                      : 250,000,000
IPO price (baht)                         : 28.00
Business description                     :
CBG is a Holding Company; it's mainly invested in subsidiaries as Carabao Tawan 
Dang Co., Ltd. (CBD), Tawandang DCM Co.,Ltd. (DCM) and Asia Pacific Glass Co.,
Ltd. (APG). A core subsidiary is CBD. Those are operating in production,
distribution, and sale and marketing of Carabao Dang-brand energy drinks and
START Plus Zinc.
Remark                                   :
-IPO 250,000,000 shares, divided into 100,000,000 existing ordinary shares and 
150,000,000 new ordinary shares.
